Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.21,0:00:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想打從心裡大叫一句\N好想快點見到妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.16,0:00:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信總有一天\N一定能相遇相知永結連理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.81,0:00:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起步走出\N希望妳能追著我的背影而來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.12,0:00:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我孤單一人只為等候妳的到來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.30,0:01:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落英繽紛的春日午後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.28,0:01:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我將祈禱轉為誓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.25,0:01:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但願妳不會忘記最重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.46,0:01:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠閃亮動人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.68,0:01:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了,請等一下哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.92,0:01:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.46,0:01:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問是哪位?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.89,0:01:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.83,0:02:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.10,0:02:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公,響子來看你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.94,0:02:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.88,0:02:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.78,0:02:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,感冒好點了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.65,0:02:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳來看我了啊,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.85,0:02:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到妳來,我突然就好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.29,0:02:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪,好像連燒都退了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.96,0:02:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.04,0:02:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#94 太好了!五代決死的求婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.75,0:02:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後來怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.42,0:02:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.38,0:02:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是妳跟一刻館\N那個五代的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.63,0:03:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響…響子,妳該不會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.37,0:03:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟那個叫什麼來著的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.30,0:03:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公,他叫五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.54,0:03:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳跟他在交往嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.51,0:03:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,反正你們遲早會知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.99,0:03:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我不答應!\N-我猜得果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.46,0:03:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳終於想再婚啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.43,0:03:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊\N不過,他還沒正式跟我求婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.64,0:03:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准!不准!不准!\N我絕對不答應!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.92,0:04:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,累垮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.19,0:04:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊,真的煩死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.43,0:04:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我以前有勸你進這一行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.30,0:04:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,薪水很少哦\N你知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.10,0:04:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對一個剛被正式錄取的人\N妳別嚇他好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.04,0:04:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一他現在辭職\N我們也會很困擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.47,0:04:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真想早點結婚辭掉工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.44,0:04:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真羨慕妳\N已經決定要結婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.51,0:04:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,暫時兩個人\N還都要工作賺錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.55,0:04:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當初他是怎麼向妳求婚的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.05,0:04:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.32,0:04:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們兩個交往很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.43,0:04:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他問我“差不多要不要結婚了?”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.93,0:04:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就回答“好啊”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.33,0:04:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.63,0:04:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉麵店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.47,0:04:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛,真是沒情調
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.64,0:04:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.77,0:04:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少也該浪漫一點嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.41,0:05:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,這也無所謂\N嫁得出去就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.65,0:05:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你有興趣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.82,0:05:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,你在想結婚的事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.36,0:05:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.36,0:05:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊,你有對象啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.46,0:05:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次來找你的人對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.56,0:05:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,我也想趕快向她求婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.60,0:05:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是一直找不到適當的時機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.44,0:05:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也想不出什麼浪漫的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.21,0:05:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是不能老是讓她等,對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.81,0:05:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看還是今晚向她求婚好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.98,0:05:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走了,工作工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.22,0:05:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,把杯子洗一洗哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.37,0:05:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.97,0:05:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛,那麼不講理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.04,0:06:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管爸爸怎麼反對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.31,0:06:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要跟五代…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.28,0:06:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,他要到什麼時候\N才會向我求婚呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.49,0:06:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳嫁給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.00,0:06:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太平凡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.03,0:06:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然要說,就要說特別一點的\N感覺才比較不會假假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.87,0:06:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,請跟我進同樣的墳墓吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.31,0:06:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行,太不吉利了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.68,0:06:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳成為五代響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.28,0:06:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好難為情哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.20,0:07:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,味噌湯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.20,0:07:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請為我煮味噌湯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.91,0:07:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.78,0:07:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就用這個!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.99,0:07:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.36,0:07:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以進來一下嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.83,0:07:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.80,0:07:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那個…\N-什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.55,0:07:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響…響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.65,0:07:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.82,0:08:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請為我…味噌…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.00,0:08:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放輕鬆,放輕鬆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.04,0:08:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.34,0:08:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.12,0:08:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不是來向我求婚的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.83,0:08:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要再喝點茶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.80,0:08:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想喝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.70,0:08:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想喝味噌湯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.48,0:08:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.61,0:08:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.48,0:08:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我想喝響子…\N響子煮的味噌湯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.32,0:09:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想喝妳煮的味噌湯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.26,0:09:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.30,0:09:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,我剛好留了一點\N準備當惣一郎的早餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.97,0:09:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了,飯也還有剩哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.01,0:09:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不用了,味噌湯就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.12,0:09:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,真好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.85,0:09:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.46,0:09:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我差點忘了,響子一向很遲鈍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.89,0:09:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種婉轉的說法\N對她是行不通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.93,0:09:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須得直接跟她說\N“請妳嫁給我吧”才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響…響子,請妳跟我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.04,0:09:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.04,0:09:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳跟我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.21,0:10:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宴會開始囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.21,0:10:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你在這裡幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.18,0:10:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不行哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.62,0:10:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為光靠一碗味噌湯\N就能渡過這個寒冷夜晚嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.17,0:10:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代那個笨蛋,真的笨死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.00,0:10:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員\N管理員,我在叫妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.07,0:10:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.91,0:10:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電話響了很久了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.41,0:10:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.18,0:10:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?爸爸他?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.85,0:10:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,偷偷溜出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.66,0:10:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他明明還在發燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.73,0:10:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該不可能去找妳\N不過如果他去找妳,那就麻煩妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.23,0:10:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了,如果他來了\N我會馬上帶他回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.27,0:10:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.44,0:11:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳爸爸怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.07,0:11:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,沒有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.54,0:11:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是想幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.61,0:11:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是來反對我們結婚?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.95,0:11:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點爬上來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.75,0:11:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪,那傢伙是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.86,0:11:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不答應你們結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.07,0:11:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要親口拒絕這門婚事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.38,0:11:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?妳爸爸不見了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.55,0:11:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.41,0:11:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊\N他本來發高燒躺在床上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.42,0:11:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說,我想…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.72,0:11:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說不定會去找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.93,0:11:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我昨天跟他說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.66,0:12:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你在交往的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.27,0:12:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.87,0:12:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.14,0:12:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他來的話\N我會立刻跟妳聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.78,0:12:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.46,0:12:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以響子的爸爸那種個性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.06,0:12:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他真來了的話\N一定是來反對我們結婚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.34,0:12:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才不是說了嗎\N我不是變態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.32,0:12:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你站在那個地方\N到底想幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.23,0:13:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,我要背背
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.50,0:13:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背背?好,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.57,0:13:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,爸爸的背好溫暖哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.04,0:13:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.34,0:13:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,優美,妳也很溫暖哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.34,0:13:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那爸爸你也不冷囉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.54,0:13:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,一點都不冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.45,0:13:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,我要背背
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.76,0:13:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等妳長大了之後\N換妳來背爸爸好不好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.73,0:13:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.90,0:13:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要,爸爸好重哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.43,0:13:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會把我壓扁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.74,0:13:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓妳的新郎來背我好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.31,0:13:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要,我才不要嫁人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.84,0:13:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.28,0:14:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.20,0:14:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,結果妳爸爸沒有來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.60,0:14:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,如果他來這裡\N我一定會通知妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.87,0:14:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然妳爸爸出事了,對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.24,0:14:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.81,0:14:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,由加,這個送給妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.92,0:14:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝部長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.18,0:14:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看哦,送給小雛的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.55,0:14:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一隻小熊貓哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.52,0:14:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒哦,好棒哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.46,0:14:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很棒吧,部長送給我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.80,0:14:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,這是你做的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.50,0:14:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的手藝還是一樣行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.70,0:14:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡,我能留給他們的\N也只有這些了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.54,0:14:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是餞別啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.84,0:14:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.34,0:15:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是餞別?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.31,0:15:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不懂沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.15,0:15:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.22,0:15:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有訪客哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.39,0:15:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,進來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.70,0:15:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.61,0:15:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我問你\N你想對我們家響子怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.49,0:15:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來我是想\N等正式向響子求婚之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.49,0:15:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後再到府上拜訪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.69,0:15:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟響子結…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.06,0:15:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要說了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.26,0:15:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼能眼睜睜的\N看著響子陷入不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.03,0:15:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不會呢,我向您保證\N我一定會讓她幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.34,0:16:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說這種不負責任的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.64,0:16:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你們結婚了\N也絕對不會幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.11,0:16:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.95,0:16:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說完了,我要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.32,0:16:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.76,0:16:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她老爸一定很震驚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.63,0:16:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看五代跟管理員\N是不可能在一起了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.10,0:16:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代的春天\N結果還是沒有來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.81,0:16:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸那個笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.28,0:16:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做到這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.62,0:16:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.32,0:16:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候\N爸爸該怎麼做才好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.53,0:16:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道會讓妳這麼痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.46,0:17:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當初我就應該更加地…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.27,0:17:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反對妳結婚才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.44,0:17:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要嫁人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.71,0:17:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不要嫁人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.48,0:17:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不要嫁人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.14,0:17:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不要嫁人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.12,0:17:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.79,0:17:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.33,0:17:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這叫我怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.73,0:17:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老伯,你復活啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.83,0:17:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,就正式開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.74,0:17:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.94,0:17:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.58,0:17:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.78,0:17:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長,隨時都歡迎你回來唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.95,0:17:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼啊\N我們得好好幫他送別才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.95,0:17:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎喲,大叔\N你也別臭著一張臉嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.16,0:18:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.03,0:18:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要你管!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.57,0:18:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.17,0:18:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長,你真的要走了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.51,0:18:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要你走!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.98,0:18:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家不可以這麼任性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.72,0:18:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要走!部長!不要走!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.96,0:18:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔,你怎麼跟著哭起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.10,0:18:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是部長新的人生起點耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.30,0:18:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要開心地歡送他才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.90,0:18:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟這是一件喜事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.45,0:18:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哭不是為了這個!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.12,0:19:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不想再看到\N響子哭泣的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.59,0:19:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.86,0:19:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.34,0:19:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.97,0:19:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡說什麼啊\N我為什麼要哭呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.88,0:19:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真傻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.57,0:19:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,我馬上叫計程車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.71,0:20:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必了,反正很近\N我背他回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.58,0:20:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,爸爸真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.76,0:20:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有沒有對你\N說什麼難聽的話?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.16,0:20:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.50,0:20:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來妳爸爸很擔心妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.81,0:20:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對妳爸爸而言,響子妳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.24,0:20:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠都是個小女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.45,0:20:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小女孩的響子…啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.73,0:20:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.76,0:20:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.13,0:21:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是我唯一的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.48,0:21:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳嫁給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.13,0:21:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會做出\N會讓妳哭泣的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.76,0:22:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳將今後的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.43,0:22:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交付給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.67,0:22:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只要你答應我一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.15,0:22:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.45,0:22:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.72,0:22:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕只是多一天也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.59,0:22:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要活得比我久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.03,0:22:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再一個人\N孤零零的活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.84,0:22:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.72,0:22:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會放下妳一個人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.36,0:22:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.89,0:23:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.66,0:23:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,如果妳討厭這小子的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.43,0:23:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都可以回來哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.77,0:23:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.74,0:23:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,他們回新瀉老家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.14,0:23:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是五代的爸媽會答應嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.98,0:23:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年紀比五代大\N而且又是第二次結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.75,0:23:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心啦,響子沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.88,0:24:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.45,0:24:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「啊～感動!\N包含於戒指中的奶奶之愛」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.12,0:24:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.23,0:24:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the night
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.96,0:24:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin your love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.17,0:24:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳該知道這不是擦身而過的戀情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.11,0:24:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親吻也是…woo
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.32,0:24:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳比我想像中冷淡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.52,0:24:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡一個人獨處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.19,0:24:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉默不語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.06,0:24:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要逞強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.84,0:24:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這燭火依偎著的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.98,0:25:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凝視著妳的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.92,0:25:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試著將至今的謊言吹熄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:15.76,0:25:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the night
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:19.50,0:25:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin your love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:22.63,0:25:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自我陶醉故弄玄虛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:27.00,0:25:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我行不通…woo
